      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, providing tactile shift throws and a direct connection to the rear-biased Variable M Differential Lock. Significant enthusiast-grade maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and reinforced rear subframe mounts to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension has been sharpened with upgraded dampers, while the cross-drilled rotors and multi-piston calipers provide consistent thermal management. This is a driver-focused machine with excellent mechanical compression and a clean power delivery through the entire RPM range.",
